  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  age ≥ 18 years and &lt;75 years

          -  FSHD patients 1 or 2 with genetic confirmation

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Phosphokinase creatine level &gt; 5 time of the normal

          -  Patient as medical history :

               -  A history or active neurological disease likely to interfere with the
                  interpretation of results

               -  a history of head trauma

               -  an infectious disease, hormonal, inflammatory or some deficiency may induce
                  cognitive and / or psychiatric troubles

               -  Patient with cons-indication for performing a brain MRI

          -  Pregnant, parturient and lactating (producing a serum pregnancy test)
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
